  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This randomised controlled trial aims to investigate the efficacy of fenugreek wraps in the
      treatment of primary symptomatic osteoarthritis of the knee. 81 patients will be randomised
      into one of 3 groups and apply fenugreek wraps or diclofenac gel daily for 4 weeks or receive
      only usual care. Efficacy will be measured using questionnaire on pain, disability,function,
      quality of life and pressure pain sensitivity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
